= Project Costs: Where Donations are Needed =
--> [:FfiiprojEn: Projects], [http://www.ffii.org/assoc/financ/konto/ Donate], [:PagExamEn: Financial Examination]
----

== Purpose of this Project  ==

 * List and prioritise the items for which funds raised by FFII should be used.
 * develop workable rules for compensating some of the costs of our helpers

== Items which Need Donations Most ==

 1. reimburse expenses (travel and lodging) for worthwhile activities all over Europe  
   * many trips needed in coming months
   * [http://plone.ffii.org/events/2004/test/ november conference in Brussels will cost 20,000 eur]                   
 1. [:BruRepEn: permanent Brussels representation] (partly covered by OSI grant)
 1. [:PrmatEn: PR Materials]: create nice PR materials, including cartoons, brochures, [:ConsVideo0405En: video sequences], MEP welcome pack
 1. [:MediaEn: Media Work]; push existing ffii infos into the media, assist those who want to help, buy mindshare  
 1. [:PolisEn: Computing]:
   * [:AktivEn: Participation System] et al need regular programming work to create new applications  
   * better hardware is needed to cope with load
   * [:PatdbEn: patent database]
 1. routine work that volunteers usually don't like to do 

== Modes of Payment ==

 * based on invoices submitted to an [:PagExamEn: examination committee], with reference to work done and hours spent
 * [http://www.ffii.org/assoc/financ/account/ How to Donate]
